":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCursing a believer is like killing him.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 762 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0646\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23939,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/31\/cursing-takfir-like-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":32151,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Takfir: Excommunicating a Muslim like killing him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a man declares his brother to be an unbeliever, it is as if he has killed him. Cursing a believer is like killing him.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 3158 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15853,"url":